# Overview

* 本文件說明地圖編輯器使用的API，供第三方重寫後端服務，確保行為一致

* 建議搭配MongoDB，確保資料結構與原服務一致

* Generic error codes and messages

# Database Schema

API共使用到兩個Mongo collection，請確保資料結構一致

1. Map (地圖主表)

* 本資料表用於儲存系統中所有地圖相關資訊

* 資料結構如下

|Field|Type|Description|
|:----|:----|:----|
|_id|ObjectID||
|name|String|地圖名稱|
|origin|Array|座標偏移量|
|resolution|Double|地圖分辨率|
|points|Array |存放location.yaml裡的地標點|
|graph|String|存放graph.yaml內容|
|door|String|存放door.yaml內容|
|location|String|存放location.yaml內容|
|virtual_wall|String|存放virtuall_wall.yaml內容|
|zone|String|存放zone.yaml內容|
|map|String||
|bgm|String|底圖 (S3 Objectkey)|
|eraseKey|String|橡皮擦區域圖 (S3 Objectkey)|
|file|String|打包後的地圖檔 (S3 Objectkey)|
|createdAt|Int|初次新增地圖時戳|
|updatedAt|Int|更新地圖時戳|
|note|Object|存放map.json內容|

# API Overview

請實作以下API，以提供地圖編輯器進行地圖查詢、複製與修改等核心功能

||Name|Method|Path|
|:----|:----|:----|:----|
|1|獲取單個地圖詳情|GET|/v1/mapAPI/map/group/:mapId|
|2|獲取地圖歷史版本|GET|/v1/mapAPI/map/group/:mapId/version|
|3|複製地圖|POST|/v1/mapAPI/cp/map/:mapId|
|4|更新地圖|PUT|/v1/mapAPI/map/yaml/:mapId|

###  3 複製地圖

本API用於將既有地圖資料完整複製為新地圖， 複製後之地圖將產生新的唯一識別碼， 與原始地圖相互獨立，後續修改互不影響

######  3.1 請求方式

>POST /v1/mapAPI/cp/map/:mapId
######  3.2 請求參數

```json
Header
  Content-Type: application/json
```
######  3.3 回應

```json
// successful
HTTP_CODE=200
{
    "status": {
        "code": "0",
        "message": "OK",
        "description": "copy map successful."
    },
    "data": {
        "_id": "532c05aa80cdcbd5d7a7bcd9" // 新產生的地圖id
    }
}

// faulure
HTTP_CODE=400
{
    "status": {
        "code": "10008",
        "message": "OPERATION_FAILED",
        "description": "Not found the mapId."
    },
    "data": null
}
```
######  3.4 邏輯說明

![img](data:image/png;base64,)
1. 後端對MongoDB發出請求，查詢地圖資訊，取得Map Object

2. 取得Map Object後，向S3發出GetObject請求，下載地圖zip檔

3. 取得地圖zip檔後，解壓縮地圖檔

4. 上傳背景圖map.jpg與橡皮擦區域map_erase_area.jpg到S3，取得新的Obectkey

5. 將bgm轉成base64後更新graph.yaml

6. 更新地圖資訊的bgm與eraseKey屬性

7. 將新的地圖新增至MongoDB，並取得返回的ObjectId

8. 替換壓縮檔裡map.json的uuid屬性，uuid value替換成新的地圖Objectid，

9. 更新DB note欄位

10. 重新壓縮zip檔

11. 將zip檔上傳到S3，取得新的Obectkey

12. 更新DB file欄位

13. 返回新地圖的Objectid給前端

######  3.5 範例

```javascript
cloneRMSMapAsync = async (ctx) => {
    const params = ctx.request.params;
    const mapId = params.mapId;
    const now = utils.retNowTimestamp();
    const workspace = this._workspaceGenerator('export');

    try {
        let filter = {
            _id: ObjectID(mapId)
        };
        // 撈取地圖資訊
        let map = await mapDAO.getMapAsync(filter);
        if (!map) {
            return utils.failureFormart(message.c30001, ctx);
        }
        delete map._id;
        
        await fileHelper.mkdir(workspace);
        // download map file form s3
        let zipPath = await this._donwloadAndUnzipMapAsync(workspace, map);
        // 上傳底圖與橡皮擦區域圖到S3
        await this._uploadBgmAndErasepAsync(workspace, map);

        map.name = `${map.name} 副本`;
        map.createdAt = now;
        map.updatedAt = now;
        let result = await mapDAO.addMapAsync(map);
        await this._updateMapAndZipAsync(result.insertedId, zipPath, workspace, map);
        let response = {
            _id: result.insertedId
        };
        ctx.body = utils.successFormat(response);
        return;
    } catch (err) {
        await systemErrorHandle(err, ctx);
    }
};

/**
 * @desc 更新底圖與橡皮擦區域圖
 */
_uploadBgmAndErasepAsync = async (workspace, map) => {
    let filename = path.parse(map.file).name;
    let graphPath = `${workspace}/${filename}/graph.yaml`;
    let graphYaml = await fileHelper.read(graphPath);
    graphYaml = graphYaml.toString();
    let bgmPath = `${workspace}/${filename}/map.jpg`;

    // 上傳map.jpg與map_erase_area.png到S3
    if (await fileHelper.exists(bgmPath)) {       
        map.bgm = await this._uploadResourceToCloudAsync('map.jpg', bgmPath);
        // 將bgm轉成base64後，更新graph.yaml
        graphYaml = await this._parserBackground(graphYaml, map, bgmPath);
        await fileHelper.writeStream(graphPath, graphYaml);
        map.graph = graphYaml;
    }
    let erasePath = `${workspace}/${filename}/map_erase_area.png`;
    if (await fileHelper.exists(erasePath)) {
        map.eraseKey = await this._uploadResourceToCloudAsync('map_erase_area.png', erasePath);
    }
};

_parserBackground = (yamlBody, body, output) => {
    let drawing = `    drawing:\n      filename: ${path.parse(body.bgm).name}`;
    let regex = /[^\S\n]{4}(drawing:)\n[^\S\n]{6}(filename:)([a-zA-Z0-9_ :\/;,+=]*)/;
    yamlBody = yamlBody.replace(regex, drawing);
    let base64 = `    cache:\n      filename: data:image/png;base64,`;
    base64 += fileHelper.imgToBase64(output);
    regex = /[^\S\n]{4}(cache:)\n[^\S\n]{6}(filename:)([a-zA-Z0-9_ :\/;,+=]*)/;
    yamlBody = yamlBody.replace(regex, base64);
    return yamlBody;
};

/**
 * @desc 重新打包地圖zip
 */
_updateMapAndZipAsync = async (lastInsertId, zipPath, workspace, map) => {
    let objectKey = lastInsertId.toString();
    // 更新map.json裡的uuid屬性
    await this._updateMapJSONAsync(workspace, map, objectKey);

    // 打包地圖目錄下的所有檔案
    let filename = path.parse(map.file).name;
    let outputName = `${path.parse(map.file).name}.zip`;
    await this._addFileToZip(outputName);

    let zipfile = `${workspace}/${filename}/${map.file}`;
    // 上傳地圖zip到S3
    let file = await this._uploadResourceToCloudAsync(map.file, zipfile);

    let updateBody = {
        file: file,
        note: map.note
    };
    // 更新DB
    await this._updateMapAsync(lastInsertId, updateBody);
};

_updateMapJSONAsync = async (workspace, map, mapId) => {
    let filename = path.parse(map.file).name;
    let notePath = `${workspace}/${filename}/map.json`;
    if (await fileHelper.exists(notePath)) {
        let buf = await fileHelper.read(notePath);
        let regex = /"uuid":\s*(?:"([^"]*)"|(\S+))/;
        let mapBody = buf.toString('utf8');

        let found = mapBody.match(regex);
        if (found) {
            let str = '"uuid":"' + mapId + '"';
            mapBody = mapBody.replace(regex, str);
        } else {
            mapBody = JSON.parse(mapBody);
            mapBody['uuid'] = mapId;
            mapBody = JSON.stringify(mapBody);
        }

        await fileHelper.writeStream(notePath, mapBody);
        map.note = await this._findMapNoteAsync(notePath);
    }
};
```
###  4 更新地圖

本API用於更新既有地圖之基本資訊與腳本內容 

######  4.1 請求方式

>PUT /v1/mapAPI/map/yaml/:mapId
######  4.2 請求參數

```json
Header
  Content-Type: multipart/form-data
```
###### Form data

|Field|Type|Required|Describe|
|:----|:----|:----|:----|
|file|File|Y|graph.yaml|
|base|File|N|底圖|
|map_erase_area|File|N|橡皮擦區域圖|
|location|File|Y|location.yaml|
|virtual_wall|File|Y|virtual_wall.yaml|
|zone|File|Y|zone.yaml|
|door|File|Y|door.yaml|
|name|String|N|地圖名稱|
|map_version|Number|N|地圖版本|
|origin|Array|N|座標|
|resolution|Number|N|解析度|
|note|Object|N|描述檔|

######  4.3 回應

```json
// successful
HTTP_CODE=200
{
    "status": {
        "code": "0",
        "message": "OK",
        "description": "update map successful."
    },
    "data": {
        "updatedAt": 1770278898 // 返回更新時的時間
    }
}

// faulure
HTTP_CODE=400
{
    "status": {
        "code": "10008",
        "message": "OPERATION_FAILED",
        "description": "Not found the mapId."
    },
    "data": null
}
```
######  4.4 邏輯說明

![img](data:image/png;base64,)
1. 後端對MongoDB發出請求，查詢地圖資訊，取得Map Object

2. 若上傳file欄位 (graph.yaml)，需檢查origin與原地圖的origin是否不同，如有變更則不允許更新地圖

3. 取得Map Object後，向S3發出GetObject請求，下載地圖zip檔

4. 取得地圖zip檔後，解壓縮地圖檔

5. 處理上傳的yaml檔

      5.1 如有上傳file欄位 (graph.yaml) 且有上傳map_version欄位，則需更新graph.yaml檔案的map_version value，並更新Map Object graph value

      5.2 如有上傳map_erase_area欄位，將檔案上傳至S3後更新Map Object eraseKey value

      5.3 如有上傳location欄位，更新Map Object location value後，再取得location檔案裡的座標，更新Map Object points value

      5.4 如有上傳virtual_wall欄位，更新Map Object virtual_wall value

      5.5 如有上傳zone欄位，更新Map Object zone value

      5.6 如有上傳door欄位，更新Map Object door value 

      5.7 如有上傳其他屬性，有一樣更新需Map Object

6. 重新壓縮zip檔

7. 將zip檔上傳到S3，取得新的Obectkey

8. 更新DB file欄位

9. 返回此次更新時戳 (秒)

######  4.5 範例

```javascript
putRMSMapAsync = async (ctx) => {
    const params = ctx.request.params;
    const mapId = params.mapId;
    const files = ctx.request.files;
    const body = ctx.request.body;
    const now = utils.retNowTimestamp();
    const workspace = this._workspaceGenerator('export');
    let updateBody = {};
    let graphBody = '';

    try {
        let filter = {
            _id: ObjectID(mapId),
        };
        let map = await mapDAO.getMapAsync(filter);
        if (!map) {
            return utils.failureFormart(message.c30001, ctx);
        }

        // 若有傳入graph.yaml，則檢查origin是否有變更，如有變更則不允許更新地圖
        if (files.file) {
            let file = await fileHelper.read(files.file.path, 'utf8');
            let graphYaml = yaml.parse(file.toString());
            let origin = graphYaml?.levels?.L1?.origin;
            if (!origin) {
                throw new DidKeyError(message.c30010);
            }
            for (let i = 0; i < origin.length; i++) {
                if (origin[i] !== map.origin[i]) {
                    throw new DidKeyError(message.c30011);
                }
            }
        }

        let objectKey = `${config.uploadFieldKey}${map.file}`;
        let fileName = path.basename(objectKey);
        let name = path.parse(fileName).name;
        let distPath = `${workspace}/${name}`;

        // 下載地圖zip檔並解壓縮
        await fileHelper.mkdir(workspace);
        await this._donwloadAndUnzipMapAsync(workspace, map);

        // upload graph.yaml
        if (files.file) {
            let rl = await fileHelper.readline(files.file.path);
            graphBody = await this._fetchGraphYaml(rl);
            let dist = `${distPath}/graph.yaml`;
            if (body.map_version) {
                graphBody = await this._fetchMapYamlVersion(graphBody, body.map_version, now);
            }
            await fileHelper.writeStream(dist, graphBody);
            updateBody.graph = graphBody;
        }
        // upload map_erase_area.png
        if (files.map_erase_area) {
            let eraseName = 'map_erase_area.png';
            let erasePath = `${distPath}/${eraseName}`;
            await fileHelper.copy(files.map_erase_area.path, erasePath);
            updateBody.eraseKey = await this._uploadResourceToCloudAsync(eraseName, erasePath);
        }
        // upload location.yaml
        if (files.location) {
            let buf = await fileHelper.read(files.location.path);
            let content = buf.toString('utf8');
            content = content.replace(/\n+$/, '');
            let dist = `${distPath}/location.yaml`;
            await fileHelper.writeStream(dist, content);
            let yamlContent = yaml.parse(content);
            let points = this._parserLocationYaml(yamlContent);
            updateBody.location = content;
            updateBody.points = points;
        }
        // upload virtual_wall.yaml
        if (files.virtual_wall) {
            let buf = await fileHelper.read(files.virtual_wall.path);
            let content = buf.toString('utf8');
            content = content.replace(/\n+$/, '');
            let dist = `${distPath}/virtuall_wall.yaml`;
            await fileHelper.writeStream(dist, content);
            updateBody.virtual_wall = content;
        }
        // upload zone.yaml
        if (files.zone) {
            let buf = await fileHelper.read(files.zone.path);
            let content = buf.toString('utf8');
            content = content.replace(/\n+$/, '');
            let dist = `${distPath}/zone.yaml`;
            await fileHelper.writeStream(dist, content);
            updateBody.zone = content;
        }
        // upload door.yaml
        if (files.door) {
            let buf = await fileHelper.read(files.door.path);
            let content = buf.toString('utf8');
            content = content.replace(/\n+$/, '');
            let dist = `${distPath}/door.yaml`;
            await fileHelper.writeStream(dist, content);
            updateBody.door = content;
        }
        if (body.name) {
            // 更新map.json裡的地圖名稱
            let file = await fileHelper.read(`${distPath}/map.json`, 'utf8');
            let mapJson = JSON.parse(file.toString());
            mapJson.name = body.name;
            await fileHelper.write(`${distPath}/map.json`, JSON.stringify(mapJson));
            updateBody.name = body.name;
        }
        if (body.origin) {
            updateBody.origin = JSON.parse(body.origin);
        }
        if (body.note) {
            await fileHelper.write(`${distPath}/map.json`, body.note);
            updateBody.note = JSON.parse(body.note);
        }
        if (body.resolution) {
            updateBody.resolution = parseFloat(body.resolution);
        }

        // 打包地圖目錄下的所有檔案
        let mapName = map.map && typeof map.map === 'string' ? path.parse(map.map).name : 'map';
        let outputName = `${mapName}.zip`;
        await this._addFileToZip(outputName);

        // 上傳zip包到S3
        let outputPath = `${distPath}/${outputName}`; 
        let sourceKey = new ObjectID().toHexString();
        let mapKey = await this._uploadResourceToCloudAsync(outputName, outputPath, sourceKey);
        updateBody.file = mapKey;
        updateBody.updatedAt = now;
        map.updatedAt = updateBody.updatedAt;

        await mapDAO.updateMapAsync(filter, updateBody);
        ctx.body = utils.successFormat({
            updatedAt: map.updatedAt
        });
        return;
    } catch (err) {
        await systemErrorHandle(err, ctx);
    }
};

/**
 * @desc 更新map.json的map_version
 */
_fetchMapYamlVersion = async (yamlBody, mapYamlVersion, version) => {
    let regex1 = /map_version: \d+\.\d+|map_version: \d+/;
    let found1 = yamlBody.match(regex1);
    if (found1) {
        let versionBody = `map_version: ${mapYamlVersion}`;
        yamlBody = yamlBody.replace(regex1, versionBody);
    } else {
        let regex2 = /[^\S\n]{4}(version:)([a-zA-Z0-9_ :\/;,+=]*)/;
        let found2 = yamlBody.match(regex2);
        if (found2) {
            let versionBody = `    version: ${version}\n`;
            versionBody += `    map_version: ${mapYamlVersion}`;
            yamlBody = yamlBody.replace(regex2, versionBody);
        } else {
            let regex3 = /lifts: {}/;
            let found3 = yamlBody.match(regex3);
            if (found3) {
                let versionBody = `    version: ${version}\n`;
                versionBody += `    map_version: ${mapYamlVersion}\n`;
                versionBody += `lifts: {}`;
                yamlBody = yamlBody.replace(regex3, versionBody);
            }
        }
    }
    return yamlBody;
};
```
